        correct: 1,
        rationale: "Anti-TNF agents suppress macrophage-mediated granuloma containment of Mycobacterium tuberculosis. Screening for latent TB with IGRA or PPD is mandatory before starting any anti-TNF biologic, as reactivation TB is a serious and potentially fatal complication."
